{"word":"G3807 - παιδαγωγός - paidagōgós - pahee-dag-o-gos' - Instructor","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παιδαγωγός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paidagōgós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pahee-dag-o-gos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Instructor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"உபாத்தியாயர், உபாத்தி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a tutor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3816 - παῖς - paîs - paheece/3816\">G3816</a> and a reduplication form of <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; a <i>boy leader</i>, that is, a servant whose office it was to take the children to school; (by implication [figuratively] a <i>tutor</i> [&ldquo;paedagogue&rdquo;]): - instructor, schoolmaster."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3807 - παιδαγωγός - paidagōgós - pahee-dag-o-gos'/3807\">G3807</a>, <a href=\"#/G3809 - παιδεία - paideía - pahee-di'-ah/3809\">G3809</a>, <a href=\"#/G3810 - παιδευτής - paideutḗs - pahee-dyoo-tace'/3810\">G3810</a>, <a href=\"#/G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o/3811\">G3811</a>, <a href=\"#/G521 - ἀπαίδευτος - apaídeutos - ap-ah'-ee-dyoo-tos/521\">G521</a>"}]}